sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Voter
    participant App as SecureVoteApp
    participant Scanner as Fingerprint Scanner
    participant API as Server API (/api/verify-prints)
    participant DB as Database
    participant AFIS as SourceAFIS Matcher

    Note over Voter,API: Start point: voter identity details already submitted and accepted for auth step

    Voter->>Scanner: Place finger on scanner
    Scanner-->>App: Captured grayscale image + quality
    App->>App: Convert grayscale image to PNG bytes
    App->>App: Build encrypted envelope {userType=voter, scannedFingerprint, voterId or candidateVoterIds}
    App->>API: POST encrypted payload to /api/verify-prints

    API->>API: Decrypt envelope and validate request fields

    alt Single voter flow (voterId provided)
        API->>DB: Load voter by voterId
        DB-->>API: Voter record + encrypted stored fingerprint
        API->>API: Decrypt stored voter fingerprint
        API->>AFIS: Match(scanned, stored) with threshold=40
        AFIS-->>API: score + isMatch
    else Collision flow (candidateVoterIds provided)
        API->>DB: Load candidate voters by IDs
        DB-->>API: Candidate records
        loop For each candidate voter
            API->>API: Decrypt candidate stored fingerprint
            API->>AFIS: Match(scanned, candidateStored)
            AFIS-->>API: candidate score
        end
        API->>API: Pick first candidate with score >= 40
    end

    alt Match found and voter has not voted
        API-->>App: 200 success + isMatch=true + matchedVoterId + score
        App-->>Voter: Authentication successful (proceed)
    else Match found but voter already voted
        API-->>App: 400 already voted (official assistance required)
        App-->>Voter: Stop and call official
    else No match
        API-->>App: 400 isMatch=false + score + threshold
        App-->>Voter: Authentication failed (retry allowed)
    end
